This project is deprecated in favor of  drush Provision.

Install with:
ln -s build/build.sh build.sh
ln -s build/install.sh install.sh

build.conf.sh MUST have DOMAIN and TOPDOMAIN defined.
You may also implement hook_pre_install and hook_post_install.

Example:
DOMAIN=awesome
TOPDOMAIN=super

awesome_pre_install {
  echo "Now installing"
}
